《'''舊夢'''》是一首1996年中文流行歌曲，收录在[[台湾|台湾]]女歌手[[彭佳慧|彭佳慧]]的第一張专辑《說真心話》<ref>{{cite news |author1=中央社 陳家倫 |title=鐵肺歌后彭佳慧 在陸創演藝高峰 |url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170108002768-260404?chdtv |accessdate=2021-01-20 |work=中時新聞網 |date=2017-01-08 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128201124/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170108002768-260404?chdtv |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这首歌是《說真心話》的主打歌曲，也是彭佳慧經典金曲之一<ref>{{cite web|url=https://star.ettoday.net/news/302026|title=彭佳慧開深V飆鐵肺 辣媽放送裸背、美腿、事業線 - ETtoday星光雲 - ETtoday新聞雲|first=|last=ETtoday新聞雲|website=star.ettoday.net|access-date=2020-12-19|archive-date=2021-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524082644/https://star.ettoday.net/news/302026|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190531003397-260404?chdtv|title=田馥甄專業抱娃技能 全靠「他」養成 - 娛樂|first=|last=中時新聞網|website=中時新聞網|access-date=2020-12-19|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608052700/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190531003397-260404?chdtv|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Our Hope演唱會／彭佳慧壓軸 「總是會好的」全球首唱 |url=https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121469/5106850 |accessdate=2021-01-20 |work=世界新聞網 |date=2020-12-19 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128050027/https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121469/5106850 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

